name: Keep On Kicking
description: "Maybe they just wanted to fly a long time.." is a quote from the 2006 movie the Bridge. A documentary about people jumping off the Golden Gate Bridge. I wanted to have my board art embody our collective need to feel weightless, free of pain and connected to the love/freedom we all deserve. I'm so glad I found skateboarding. May we each find our way to flip the script, flip our situation and see the sun again. <3 Infinite Love and support to all those dealing with depression.You got this 8)
